{"tid":327394,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意1874呢首歌？","createTime":"2017-07-18T17:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T19:51:44.000Z","uid":105499,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"533ffa41d520cb82fb71bcfc7bb71966614330c0","tid":327394,"uid":105499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"音樂好悲傷 又好浪漫<br />\n中間個段音樂真係j 死"},{"pid":"63825c1dc2cb0f7559da190a29a5f34a775e9901","tid":327394,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"我鐘意1979"},{"pid":"e24338da87589a24ba390f621eb7b2c806bc9720","tid":327394,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"me but 成日想知點解係1874"},{"pid":"ad162394605e42048f9547701ce65511cb511765","tid":327394,"uid":61832,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>me but 成日想知點解係1874</blockquote><br />\n因為剛剛早一百年一個世紀"},{"pid":"4d507441a8356ebb7f2ba72fd4ec9afeaa6293a2","tid":327394,"uid":105499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:30:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>me but 成日想知點解係1874</blockquote><br />\n&ldquo;為何歌名是1874這年份，1874是多事之秋的年代，許多國家大事在那年爆發，但部份原因是Eason是在1974年出生的。<br />\n所以歌入面說「情人若寂寥地出生在1874&nbsp;，剛剛早一百年一個世紀」。<br />\nEason在歌裡的意境是，男主角至今都沒有遇到過命中註定的另一半，他傷感地想像自己的前世的戀人曾有約定，可惜結果兩個人在輪回時錯過了，他就朦朧地擬定了或許她出生在了一百年前，「莫非今生原定陪我來&nbsp;卻去了錯誤時代」。<br />\n男主角認定，假若他們出生在同一年代，儘管是1874，儘管是在戰火硝煙的年代，仍然能熱烈地去愛&nbsp;，同生共死。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://kenmok2324.blogspot.hk/2016/03/1874.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkenmok2324.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F03%2F1874.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4IccKxcDMBkg%2FQisIQ2xTcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=38a21517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://kenmok2324.blogspot.hk/2016/03/1874.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"9eb371d60849034e4d451755522c9368fd6e3e1e","tid":327394,"uid":124560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:30:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>me but 成日想知點解係1874</blockquote><br />\n因為剛剛早一百年一個世紀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d4d0e177814ffd47b3a9bc717c8e19f4a17060","tid":327394,"uid":83177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>me but 成日想知點解係1874</blockquote><br />\n陳奕迅出生於1974，<br />\n而他的情人：<br />\n「情人若寂寥地　出生在1874<br />\n剛剛早一百年　一個世紀」"},{"pid":"80f8748cdf389385dcf1d1df92f031e8e2ece406","tid":327394,"uid":42602,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:32:33.000Z","msg":"個女聲好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f820de95f548a229c7c2643d1613a977ed4f10","tid":327394,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>me but 成日想知點解係1874</blockquote><br />\n&ldquo;為何歌名是1874這年份，1874是多事之秋的年代，許多國家大事在那年爆發，但部份原因是Eason是在1974年出生的。<br />\n所以歌入面說「情人若寂寥地出生在1874&nbsp;，剛剛早一百年一個世紀」。<br />\nEason在歌裡的意境是，男主角至今都沒有遇到過命中註定的另一半，他傷感地想像自己的前世的戀人曾有約定，可惜結果兩個人在輪回時錯過了，他就朦朧地擬定了或許她出生在了一百年前，「莫非今生原定陪我來&nbsp;卻去了錯誤時代」。<br />\n男主角認定，假若他們出生在同一年代，儘管是1874，一是在戰火硝煙的年代，仍然能熱烈地去愛&nbsp;，同生共死。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://kenmok2324.blogspot.hk/2016/03/1874.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkenmok2324.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F03%2F1874.html%3Fm%3D1&d=4IccKxcDMBkg%2FQisIQ2xTcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=38a21517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://kenmok2324.blogspot.hk/2016/03/1874.html?m=1</a></blockquote><br />\n淒美，唔錯"},{"pid":"aad1a689e22a54bddfd3e4eaf8f2085bb784ea2a","tid":327394,"uid":124560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:35:32.000Z","msg":"有無聽1943？"},{"pid":"